OL,3,CCompany fined #200k after worker
OL,4,Csuffers burns to face and body in
OL,5,Cexplosion
OL,7,FA company has been fined #200,000
OL,8,Fafter one of their workers suffered
OL,9,Fburns to his face and body in an
OL,10,Felectrical explosion.
OL,12,FThe man was moving heavy duty cables
OL,13,Fwith a metal crowbar when the bar came
OL,14,Finto contact with a live electrical
OL,15,Fconductor, causing an explosion.
OL,17,FHe was contracted to work for New
OL,18,FEarth Solutions (West) Limited, also
OL,19,Fknown as Mid UK Recycling, at their
OL,20,Frecycling plant at Copper Hill
OL,21,Findustrial estate in , Lincolnshire.
