OL,3,CCompany fined #200k after worker
OL,4,Csuffers burns to face and body in
OL,5,Cexplosion
OL,7,FAs well as suffering serious burns,
OL,8,Fthe explosion caused the man to fall
OL,9,Ffrom the platform and sustain a broken
OL,10,Farm, fractured ribs and a dislocated
OL,11,Fknee cap.
OL,13,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,14,FSafety Executive (HSE) found the task
OL,15,Fwas not part of the normal workload
OL,16,Ffor the injured worker and that he had
OL,17,Fnot received any training with regards
OL,18,Fto undertaking electrical work.
