OL,3,CCompany fined #200k after worker
OL,4,Csuffers burns to face and body in
OL,5,Cexplosion
OL,7,FThe task had not been properly planned
OL,8,Fnor risk assessed and the electrical
OL,9,Fcables were not isolated before work
OL,10,Fbegan.
OL,12,FIn addition, the level of supervision
OL,13,Fprovided was inadequate and safety
OL,14,Fdevices on the electrical supply had
OL,15,Fbeen set inappropriately, prioritising
OL,16,Fcontinuity of supply over safety of
OL,17,Fthe electrical circuit.
